## File Size Threshold (400 Lines)

When a file exceeds **400 lines**, convert to a package:

```
# Before (450 lines)
bengal/core/page.py

# After (converted to package)
bengal/core/page/
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ __init__.py          # Main Page class (~50 lines)
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ page_core.py         # PageCore (~200 lines)
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ metadata.py          # PageMetadataMixin (~80 lines)
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ navigation.py        # PageNavigationMixin (~60 lines)
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ computed.py          # PageComputedMixin (~100 lines)
в””в”Ђв”Ђ proxy.py             # PageProxy (~150 lines)
```

